This build of sollya 8.0 is based on GMP 6.3.0, MPFR 4.2.2 and MPFI 1.5.4.
It uses FPLLL as: "fplll.h lies directly in the include directory, linkage with -lfplll is compatible, -std option is passed (-std=c++11), using standard API."

B: 16
hi_bits: 32
r_i formula: c_i = 1 + (i + 1/2) / B r_i = round(1 / c_i, D, RN)
approximated value: a_i = -log2(r_i)
split rounding: a_hi = round(a_i, hi_bits, RN) a_lo = round(a_i - a_hi, D, RN)
split invariant: a_i is approximated by a_hi + a_lo for the teaching fast path
bucket sampling: 1025 points on each closed bucket interval
